Package org.neo4j.kernel.api.impl.fulltext

Class FulltextIndexTransactionStateVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.storageengine.api.txstate.TxStateVisitor.Adapter
      • org.neo4j.kernel.api.impl.fulltext.FulltextIndexTransactionStateVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, TxStateVisitor
    class FulltextIndexTransactionStateVisitor
extends TxStateVisitor.Adapter
    A TxStateVisitor that adds all entities to a TransactionStateLuceneIndexWriter, that matches the index according to the FulltextSchemaDescriptor.
